channel.title: Barbarian Dragon Slayer and spiked skull miror shiled thingy
channel.description:
Barbarian Dragon Slayer, thats what i call it, not simple recolor, but not too much work put into it either, im hopeless at ints so don't ask for them rep the guy that adds them in this thread lol. Download Link.
Id like to see some comments first, critism is good but don't flame me this is my first model. and it's not just a recolor. Pictures. Front. [IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/2q3n5z6.jpg[/img] Back. [IMG]http://i37.tinypic.com/33u4sbq.jpg[/img]
[size=15pt]///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////[/size] now this was a simple non efortable model, from the cach re done, added more swirly spike things i think it was a gfx, but it looked better rotated and mounted on someones arm.
Picture. [IMG]http://i36.tinypic.com/288qopl.jpg[/img]
Don't like it say so, tell me why you don't like it ect, don't flame. If you think ive done a good job then tell me, this is my second model "don't complain".
also name them what you would call them when you would post, im hopeless at names.
